Implemented in:
- `components/controller/controller.c`

Behavior now:
- boots safe with pump off
- turns pump on for `LEVEL < 30`
- turns pump off for `LEVEL > 80`
- holds prior actuator output in the 30–80 band
- ignores short idle gaps
- forces safe-off on malformed input
- forces safe-off after `> 1000 ms` without valid input
- handles explicit `FAULT SENSOR_TIMEOUT` as safe-off timeout

